{"tid":677092,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[ZombsRoyale.io] 大家一齊玩網頁2D版大逃殺~ Zombs Royale","createTime":"2018-05-25T01:51:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T15:50:29.000Z","uid":50181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"670d484bd7119f234527970aacad65b3e18bf6c3","tid":677092,"uid":50181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T01:51:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><a href=\"http://ZombsRoyale.io\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FZombsRoyale.io&d=8P8rv8oVU7T5x%2FhCmoa3Ydr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2c97aaa1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">ZombsRoyale.io</a></strong></div></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>遊戲網頁</strong></ins>：<br />\n<a href=\"http://zombsroyale.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzombsroyale.io%2F&d=8P8rv8oVU7T5x%2FhCmoa3Ydr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2fd9c9d6\" target=\"_blank\">http://zombsroyale.io/</a><br />\n<br />\n類似Fortnite的網頁2D版大逃殺，免登入，直接玩。<br />\nFacebook / Google 登入可以記錄進度、升級換Skin。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>官方介紹影片</strong></ins>：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D4_SkASY4xQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DD4_SkASY4xQ&d=8P8rv8oVU7T5x%2FhCmoa3Ydr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=f8f1c99b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=D4_SkASY4xQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>簡介</strong></ins>：<br />\nZombsRoyale有單人(Solo)、雙人(Duo)、團隊(Squad) 三個基本模式，每場遊戲最多100人參與，殺晒所有敵人就贏。<br />\n另外有一個限時模式，只維持一段短時間，今個星期係團隊喪屍模式 (但只去到5月25日15點，所以我唔介紹)。<br />\n<br />\n遊戲裡可以執到種類的槍，包括：<br />\n突擊步槍 (AR)<br />\n衝鋒槍 (SMG)<br />\n狙擊槍 (Sniper)<br />\n散彈槍 (Shotgun)<br />\n火箭炮<br />\nMinigun<br />\n各類投擲類武器 、等等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每種槍各自有品質，又最弱到最強：<br />\n白 &lt; 綠 &lt; 藍 &lt; 紫 &lt; 金 &lt; 紅<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/-6xVs1bqNmJ0/WwdpTR0E1bI/AAAAAAAABFU/_wMrdYYXW2UqKr2uCGpqFEajf8Yt0hTHwCHMYCw/s0/firefox_2018-05-25_09-39-25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2F-6xVs1bqNmJ0%2FWwdpTR0E1bI%2FAAAAAAAABFU%2F_wMrdYYXW2UqKr2uCGpqFEajf8Yt0hTHwCHMYCw%2Fs0%2Ffirefox_2018-05-25_09-39-25.png&h=e730de3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果有多人有性趣一齊玩先開discord玩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>遊戲截圖</strong></ins>：<br />\n(我網上求其搵)<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/r6r23FLkSik/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fr6r23FLkSik%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=b79e8ace&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://1079638729.rsc.cdn77.org/androidgame_img/zombs_royaleio_2d_battle_royale/real/5_zombs_royaleio_2d_battle_royale.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F1079638729.rsc.cdn77.org%2Fandroidgame_img%2Fzombs_royaleio_2d_battle_royale%2Freal%2F5_zombs_royaleio_2d_battle_royale.jpg&h=35f31194&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e40400693951bcd53df8670ff9fb2de9ab93553e","tid":677092,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"lag撚到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe2aacbbbd408905d4ad9fad6d939828d4ae08df","tid":677092,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:38:12.000Z","msg":"好懷舊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc73902ca49b4477af0288fb1fcac58aa9b34cda","tid":677092,"uid":50181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e40400693951bcd53df8670ff9fb2de9ab93553e","tid":677092,"uid":240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:36:46.000Z","msg":"lag撚到傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T03:57:31.000Z","msg